PRETORIA - Getting financial investment is a problem for most sports teams, especially when it comes to women’s sport in South Africa. However, that is not so for the Tuks Ladies Sevens team. They are competently backed by Delta Drone, who sent the players to compete in tournaments in Dubai, Rome and Paris and that was just this year. eNCA’s sports reporter Shahied Joseph has more on the story. Click on the video gallery to watch the story. eNCA